# Input

```md
This paragraph
> is interrupted by block quote.

[This link
> is interrupted by block quote.](http://example.com)

[[This wiki link
> is interrupted by block quote.]]

> This is a block quote and this paragraph
>     > is interrupted neither by block quote nor indented code block.

```


